I'm pretty sure there will be plenty of &quot;police&quot; out there monitoring things. And I don't mean the MODs. I figure everytime someone looks at the VS list, they'll be sure to see if there are people on there who they've never heard of. I don't think there will be as much cheating as people suspect.<br>
<br>
Also, I'm all for the &quot;two or three guilds claiming a spot&quot; idea. I'm even for &quot;fifteen people holding a spot&quot; just so long as those names don't show up on different lists, and that they are verifiably 53+.<br>
<br>
