Stripping Indy's from that list will only take 1 rotation off.  Move it to the 50% rule and you'll only have 4 guilds on that list (SR, Enshadowed, Watchers, LoH).  Would that solve anything, no it wouldn't!  I'd be pretty pissed if Clan Spiritslammer had to give up their spot.  We've proved time and time again that we can do this raid very easily, 11 seconds is all it took to take him down one time.  I even recall once that we did Trak, Thoric was there... we all thought we failed, turns out all them wizi's paid off.  We succeeded and didn't even have to give it a 2nd try.<br>
